data.description: Bring all Offers! Introducing your perfect lake view oasis in Reeds Spring, Missouri. 2 bedroom, 2 bath with a huge loft that could be a great bunk room, craft, office, or extra living space. This home, spanning 2,132 square feet, beckons nature enthusiasts and those in search of serenity. Meticulously updated and meticulously maintained, it's ready to welcome you home. Step inside to discover an expansive master suite, a sanctuary for relaxation and rejuvenation. The attached master bath ensures your comfort, while the walk-in closet surprises with ample storage. A private deck off the suite offers a serene spot for moments of quiet reflection. Prepare to be captivated by breathtaking lake views visible from various vantage points throughout the house. Whether you're in the living area, dining space, kitchen, loft, or master, you'll be treated to a front-row seat to the natural beauty of Table Rock Lake.This home is designed for entertaining, with an open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area that creates an inviting space for hosting friends and family. Sunlight streams in through the gorgeous story and 1/2 windows in the dining/den, and a full wall of extra-large windows in the master. The 20'x30' deck is perfect for enjoying the lake view, entertaining friends or family or simply enjoying the spacious backyard that features a fire pit, ideal for creating cherished memories or watching the wildlife.No need to worry about home improvement projects - this property boasts numerous upgrades, including a maintenance-free metal-wrapped exterior trim, concrete siding, a new roof, a shiny new refrigerator, and reinforced deck supports for worry-free entertaining. The newly improved vapor barrier-wrapped, seven-foot-high crawl space adds tons of storage or maybe even a workshop/man cave. Don't forget to check out the finished interior of the extra-large 20'x30' 2-car garage.
